m\/","url_meta":{"origin":32039,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Speech: Most sins committed by the tongue","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMost of the sins of the children of Adam are on their tongues.\u201d Ibn Mas'ud said, \"O tongue! Speak goodness and be rewarded, or remain silent and be safe, lest you become regretful.\" Source: al-Mu\u2019jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/prophet-fears-sins-tongue\/","url_meta":{"origin":32039,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Speech: The Prophet fears sins of the tongue","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Sufyan ibn 'Abdillah reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, tell me of a matter I can depend upon?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: My Lord is Allah. Then, remain upright.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what do you fear most for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12005,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/04\/guard-speech-weep-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":32039,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salvation: Guard your speech, weep for your sins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 4, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what will save us?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRestrain your tongue, let your house be enough for you, and weep for your sins.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2406 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28096,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/shield-damaged-gheebah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32039,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Sins of tongue damage fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu \u2018Ubaydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting is a shield, as long as you do not damage it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2235 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Mundhiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u062c\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064c \u0645\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/sahaba-viewed-cursing-kabair\/","url_meta":{"origin":32039,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Curses: We viewed cursing brothers as major sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn Abi \u2018Ubayd reported: Salamah ibn al-Akwa\u2019, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf we saw a man curse his brother, we considered it as if he had come to a door of mortal sin.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 6674 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u064a\u064e\u0632\u0650\u064a\u062f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/06\/23\/siyam-sawm-lies-obscenity-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":32039,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: True fasting is from falsehood and sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, fasting is not only from eating and drinking. Rather, fasting is from vanity and obscenity. If someone abuses you or acts foolish against you, then say: Indeed, I am fasting.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3479\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32039"